definition: ten (used in fractions, writing checks etc)/assorted/miscellaneous
suffix, used to form interrogative 什麼|什么[shen2 me5], what?, indefinite 這麼|这么[zhe4 me5] thus, etc
what are you doing?/what's he up to?

pinyin: shen2 me5 feng1 ba3 ni3 chui1 lai2 de5

definition: it takes all sorts (to make a world) (idiom)
pinyin: lin2 zi5 da4 le5 , shen2 me5 niao3 dou1 you3

definition: it is nothing/there's nothing ... about it
nothing is impossible/there's nothing impossible about it
pinyin: mei2 you3 shen2 me5 bu4 ke3 neng2

sentences.english: What sequela is there after becoming gall-stone operation?
sentences.chinese: 做了膽結石手術後有什麼後遺症嗎？

sentences.english: What were the subtexts of this venerable tale?
sentences.chinese: 這部古老的童話所暗含的意義是什麼呢？

sentences.english: Do you know what his whereabouts are?
sentences.chinese: 你知道他現在的所在之處是什麼？

sentences.english: And why do we fall for it, year after year?
sentences.chinese: 而我們又爲什麼年復一年爲之傾倒？

sentences.english: The amount of time you spend alone has little to do with being lonely.
sentences.chinese: 你大部分獨自一人的時間想必和寂寞扯不上什麼關係。

sentences.english: Man is the only creature that consumes without producing.
sentences.chinese: 人是一種最可憐的傢伙，什麼都產不了，只會揮霍。

sentences.english: What did these tattoos look like?
sentences.chinese: 這些紋身看起來像什麼？

sentences.english: Why should cattle not graze near yew trees?
sentences.chinese: 爲什麼牛不在紫杉附近喫草？

sentences.english: She never learned how to read a milometer,or any meter.
sentences.chinese: 不管是里程錶，還是什麼表，她從來就不會看。

sentences.english: You see, I know how Kirstie feels.
sentences.chinese: 你看，我知道柯斯迪什麼感覺。

sentences.english: Where had he obtained that blouse?
sentences.chinese: 那件布罩衫，他是從什麼地方得來的呢？

sentences.english: Why should the wind do his bidding? The wind is just wind.
sentences.chinese: 爲什麼風要爲他服務呢？，風就是風。

sentences.english: What Is Unique About the Program?
sentences.chinese: 蒙氏教學方法獨特之處是什麼？

sentences.english: Which soup do you want? We have Eggdrop Soup with Sliced Tomatoes, Famous Hot &Sour Soup.
sentences.chinese: 您來點什麼湯？我們有番茄蛋花湯，酸辣湯。

sentences.english: Scientists don't yet know what the effects of those reactions might be.
sentences.chinese: 科學家們還不清楚這些反應會具體產生什麼樣的結果。

definition: suffix, used to form interrogative 什麼|什么[shen2 me5], what?, indefinite 這麼|这么[zhe4 me5] thus, etc
how?/how about?/how was it?/how are things?

that one/that thing/that (as opposed to this)/(used before a verb or adjective for emphasis)/(used to humorously or indirectly refer to sth embarrassing, funny etc, or when one can't think of the right word)/(used in speech as a filler, similar to "umm", "you know" etc)/(euph.) menstruation/sex/also pr. [nei4 ge5]
to speak/to say/to explain/to scold/to tell off/a theory (typically the last character in a compound, as in 日心說|日心说 heliocentric theory)
still/still in progress/still more/yet/even more/in addition/fairly/passably (good)/as early as/even/also/else
don't tell me .../could it be that...?
